After several minutes of silence, the "Moonlight
Sonata" started playing on the tape recorder.

235
00:13:34.326 --> 00:13:35.986
Right, Mister?

236
00:13:35.986 --> 00:13:38.306
Y-Yeah, that's right.

237
00:13:38.806 --> 00:13:45.666
