the culprit is still...

239
00:13:50.576 --> 00:13:52.806
in this room?

240
00:13:54.336 --> 00:13:58.846
Yeah, as long as they didn't
use the confusion to escape.

241
00:13:58.846 --> 00:14:00.366
Hey, Mister Detective.

242
00:14:00.626 --> 00:14:06.516
I wouldn't call it a motive, but the
man happiest about Kawashima's death

243
00:14:06.516 --> 00:14:12.236
