candidate, Shimizu-kun.

244
00:14:12.236 --> 00:14:13.706
W-What did you say?

245
00:14:13.706 --> 00:14:17.006
I could say the same thing
about you, Mayor Kuroiwa.

246
00:14:17.006 --> 00:14:17.996
What was that?

247
00:14:17.996 --> 00:14:20.276
Now, now. Try to calm down.

248
00:14:21.916 --> 00:14:25.246
By the way, how long as
that piano been here?

249
00:14:25.666 --> 00:14:30.366
It was given to the community center
as a gift from Aso-san 15 years ago.

250
00:14:30.366 --> 00:14:32.556
It's been here ever since.

251
00:14:32.556 --> 00:14:34.236
From Aso-san?

252
00:14:34.236 --> 00:14:39.026
Yes. Aso-san's name is even on the lid.

253
00:14:40.996 --> 00:14:42.216
What's this?

254
00:14:42.936 --> 00:14:43.716
Sheet music?

255
00:14:48.186 --> 00:14:52.316
