we looked at it this afternoon.

256
00:14:55.736 --> 00:14:57.736
Who was that?

257
00:14:57.736 --> 00:14:59.856
Nishimoto Ken-san.

258
00:14:59.856 --> 00:15:00.946
Nishimoto?

259
00:15:01.196 --> 00:15:04.786
He was quite prosperous a long time ago,

260
00:15:04.786 --> 00:15:07.846
but after the previous mayor
passed away two years ago,

261
00:15:07.846 --> 00:15:10.476
he began shutting himself inside his home.

262
00:15:10.926 --> 00:15:13.516
Since the incident two years ago, huh?

263
00:15:13.516 --> 00:15:18.976
Oh, right. I believe that Mayor Kuroiwa
and he are childhood friends, right?

264
00:15:19.246 --> 00:15:21.966
Yeah, I think so.

265
00:15:23.416 --> 00:15:24.616
Dad.

266
00:15:26.696 --> 00:15:28.606
I brought a police officer.

267
00:15:28.796 --> 00:15:30.756
Took you long enough, Ran.

268
00:15:30.756 --> 00:15:32.526
Yeah, but...

269
00:15:32.526 --> 00:15:36.026
Uh, who called for me?

270
00:15:36.026 --> 00:15:39.136
This man. His name is Mori Kogoro-san.

271
00:15:40.986 --> 00:15:42.686
Who are you?

272
00:15:44.736 --> 00:15:46.996
In any case, it's already late.

273
00:15:46.996 --> 00:15:49.696
We'll interview the witnesses tomorrow.

274
